#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.149"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.149:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.149:0.2"
msgid "12. Balakaraṇīyavagga "
msgstr "12. Hard Work "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.149:0.3"
msgid "149. Balasutta "
msgstr "149. Hard Work "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.46, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.149:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.149:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, all the hard work that gets done depends on the earth and is grounded on the earth. "

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.3"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path depending on and grounded on ethics. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.149:1.4"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant grounded on ethics develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path? "

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.6"
msgid "evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotīti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant grounded on ethics develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn45.149:2.1"
msgid "(Paragaṅgāpeyyālīvaṇṇiyato paripuṇṇasuttanti vitthāramaggī.) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn45.149:3.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.149:3.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.149:3.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.149:3.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ. "
msgstr "“… which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion …” "

msgctxt "sn45.149:3.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotīti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn45.149:4.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.149:4.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.149:4.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.149:4.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ. "
msgstr "“… culminate, finish, and end in the deathless …” "

msgctxt "sn45.149:4.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotīti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn45.149:5.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.149:5.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.149:5.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.149:5.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ nibbānapabbhāraṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ nibbānapabbhāraṃ. "
msgstr "“… slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment …” "

msgctxt "sn45.149:5.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.149:5.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

